graph LR
    ODHController["ODH Notebook Controller<br/>OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>+ NotebookWebhook"]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    ODHController -->|defines CRD| KubeflowController["Kubeflow Notebook Controller<br/>v0.0.0-20220728153354<br/>CRD Owner, Creates StatefulSets"]
    ODHController -->|creates| OSRoute["OpenShift Route API<br/>route.openshift.io/v1<br/>Ingress Resources"]
    ODHController -->|injects sidecar| OAuthProxy["OpenShift OAuth Proxy<br/>ose-oauth-proxy:v4.14<br/>Authentication/Authorization"]
    ODHController -->|reads| OSConfig["OpenShift Config API<br/>config.openshift.io/v1<br/>Cluster Proxy Settings"]
    ODHController -->|cert provisioning| ServiceCA["OpenShift Service CA<br/>service.beta.openshift.io<br/>Auto TLS Certificates"]
    ODHController -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>v1.29.0<br/>Services, Secrets, SA, ConfigMaps"]
    ODHController -->|network segmentation| K8sNetworking["Kubernetes Networking API<br/>networking.k8s.io/v1<br/>NetworkPolicy"]
    ODHController -->|permission mgmt| K8sRBAC["Kubernetes RBAC API<br/>rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1<br/>Roles, RoleBindings"]
    ODHController -->|framework| ControllerRuntime["controller-runtime<br/>v0.17.0<br/>Reconciliation & Webhooks"]

    %% OAuth Flow (Runtime)
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates| OAuthServer["OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>User Authentication<br/>Token Issuance"]
    OAuthProxy -->|authorization check| K8sAPI

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (Optional)
    ODHController -.->|optional RBAC| DSPA["Data Science Pipelines DSPA<br/>ds-pipeline-user-access-dspa Role<br/>Elyra Pipeline Execution"]

    %% Integration with Service Mesh (Optional)
    ODHController -.->|detection only| ServiceMesh["Service Mesh Istio<br/>mTLS, Traffic Management<br/>Annotation: service-mesh=true"]

    %% Platform Integration Points
    Dashboard["ODH Dashboard<br/>UI Management"] -.->|creates/manages| ODHController
    Users["Data Scientists"] -->|creates Notebook CR| ODHController

    %% Co-management
    KubeflowController <-->|co-manages| NotebookCR["Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1<br/>Namespaced"]
    ODHController <-->|extends via webhook| NotebookCR

    %% Created Resources (outputs)
    ODHController ==>|creates| Route["Route<br/>notebook-name"]
    ODHController ==>|creates| Service["Service<br/>notebook-name-tls"]
    ODHController ==>|creates| SA["ServiceAccount<br/>notebook-name"]
    ODHController ==>|creates| Secrets["Secrets<br/>TLS cert, OAuth config"]
    ODHController ==>|creates| NetworkPolicies["NetworkPolicies<br/>ctrl-np, oauth-np"]
    ODHController ==>|creates| RoleBindings["RoleBindings<br/>elyra-pipelines"]

    %% Styling
    style ODHController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style KubeflowController fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OSRoute fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OAuthProxy fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OSConfig fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style K8sNetworking fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style K8sRBAC fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OAuthServer fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style DSPA fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Users fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Route fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Service fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style SA fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
